'''刑天龙属'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Xingtianosaurus''}}）是一[[属|属]]已灭绝的[[偷蛋龙类|偷蛋龙类]][[兽脚亚目|兽脚亚目]][[恐龙|恐龙]]，生存於[[白垩纪|早白垩世]]的[[中国|中国]]，[[模式种|模式种]]兼唯一[[种|种]]'''干戚刑天龙'''（''X. ganqi''）于2019年命名、叙述。<ref name=Qiu2019>{{Cite journal|author1=Rui Qiu |author2=Xiaolin Wang |author3=Qiang Wang |author4=Ning Li |author5=Jialiang Zhang |author6=Yiyun Ma |year=2019 |title=A new caudipterid from the Lower Cretaceous of China with information on the evolution of the manus of Oviraptorosauria |journal=Scientific Reports |volume=9 |pages=Article number 6431 |doi=10.1038/s41598-019-42547-6 |pmid=31024012 |pmc=6483983}}</ref>它与[[尾羽龙|尾羽龙]]和[[似尾羽龙|似尾羽龙]]一起归类于[[尾羽龙科|尾羽龙科]]。<ref>Osmólska, H., Currie, P. J. & Brasbold, R. Oviraptorosauria. In The Dinosauria. 2nd edn (eds Weishampel, D., Dodson, P., & Osmólska, H.) 165–183 (University of California Press, 2004).</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Lamanna M. C., Sues H. D., Schachner E. R., Lyson T. R. | year = 2014 | title = A new large-bodied oviraptorosaurian theropod dinosaur from the Latest Cretaceous of Western North America | url = | journal = PLoS ONE | volume = 9 | issue = | page = e92022 | doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0092022 | pmid = 24647078 | pmc = 3960162}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Funston G. F., Currie P. J. | year = 2016 | title = A new caenagnathid (Dinosauria: Oviraptorosauria) from the Horseshoe Canyon Formation of Alberta, Canada, and a reevaluation of the relationships of Caenagnathidae | url = | journal = Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology | volume = 36 | issue = | page = de1160910 }}</ref>

==发现与命名==
干戚刑天龙的[[正模标本|正模标本]]'''IVPP V13390'''发现于[[中国|中国]][[辽宁省|辽宁省]][[义县组|义县组]]的大康堡层，<ref name=Qiu2019 />[[属|属名]]取自指中国传说中的[[神祇|神祇]][[刑天|刑天]]，其在被[[斩首|斩首]]后仍持续战斗――而正模标本亦缺乏头骨；[[种名|种名]]取自是指刑天挥舞的武器干戚（一种战斧）。<ref name=Qiu2019 />

==叙述==
正模标本（'''IVPP V13390'''）接近完整，只缺少[[头骨|头骨]]、几节椎骨和[[鸟喙骨|鸟喙骨]]。<ref name=Qiu2019 />

